name: Ella Freya
description:
This LoRA depicts the Youtuber Ella Freya.

She is also the face model for Ashley Graham in the video game Resident Evil 4 (2023)

My sample images were generated using Chilloutmix model.
Sampler: Euler
Steps: 60
Resolution: 512x768
CFG Scale: 7

Hires Fix is recommended.
SwinIR_4x
Denoising Strength 0.1
Upscale by 2
